{"tid":1409573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請大家記住，今日的主菜係罷工，係罷工","createTime":"2019-08-04T22:38:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T00:46:29.000Z","uid":103922,"like":70,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"90c35d57d45123c6a782833024c0c21ac7c2daf0","tid":1409573,"uid":103922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:38:30.000Z","msg":"請求行動派同勇武派係早上到下午盡量保持克制，<br />\n將行動限係不合作運動，<br />\n唔好有衝突，唔好有衝突。<br />\n一齊留意罷工的成效同影響，<br />\n如果係大的話，<br />\n希望大家可以忍一忍手，<br />\n等罷工的exposure可以有咁大去咁大，<br />\n咁罷工先有意義，<br />\n等班和理非有啲成功感，<br />\n佢地先有動力下一次再罷。<br />\n如果太早有大型衝突，<br />\n成個社會個focus會太早shift晒去衝突，<br />\n班和理非可能就會覺得做左同無做都無分別。<br />\n如果罷工成效細個社會一切運作正常，<br />\n先再諗下一步行動。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cead1e10599d4dca9314a9f50cb168ad00c473d1","tid":1409573,"uid":127013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:40:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"55ed8dd95de5896d3ea13d67d0c1a92ec2472130","tid":1409573,"uid":103922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:41:37.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79110c5a2b2d0558a24aa2e91f6de765c4ed27ff","tid":1409573,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:42:49.000Z","msg":"唔好塞到九點完，九點十點後好多中環人好想被罷工<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1409491\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1409491</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bc0b618d0f8e7b5b13c155ba86bd0cfde37ee096","tid":1409573,"uid":276715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:43:12.000Z","msg":"一齊罷"},{"pid":"ffdf20727c264682d2df4035a4980e045c6b7cb8","tid":1409573,"uid":631